snippet.title: BIOMASS: Gameplay!
snippet.description:
made in 72 hours for the cult of jabrils 5th gamejam, stay@home jam, this is a brutally difficult, surprisingly polished adventure game dropping you out of a cloning pod and into a station crawling with horrible abominations of flesh.

trailer and slightly more polished release product with mobile port coming once the game jam and voting is finished!

DOWNLOAD: 
https://brainos.itch.io/biomass
